name: Wonderland Bracelets - Blues
description:
These bracelets feature thousands of colourful glass beads that have been hand woven on soft cotton threads. They roll on for the comfiest of fit. 

These traditional Nepalese bracelets have been fairly sourced from, and handmade by, a women's beading cooperative in Nepal. Their highly-skilled work provides them with a much needed income, assisting them toward self-sufficiency and independence.

Price is per bracelet.
